  (lib_symbols)

  (text "SAFETY INTERLOCK SYSTEM\n\nFunction:\n- Over-current protection (OCP)\n- Over-voltage protection (OVP)\n- Thermal shutdown\n- Hardware watchdog\n- Logic gate combination\n- Fault latching\n\nKey Components:\n- LM339 quad comparator\n- 74HC4075 triple OR gate\n- 74HC00 quad NAND gate\n- 74HC08 quad AND gate\n- 74HC04 hex inverter\n- TPS3823-33 watchdog\n\nProtection Thresholds:\n- OCP: 40A (2.0V), 60A (3.0V)\n- OVP: 390V (divider)\n- Thermal: 85°C trip, 75°C reset\n- Watchdog: 1.6s timeout\n\nReference: SAFETY_INTERLOCK_DESIGN.md"
